# Oracle Cloud Always Free Backend Configuration
# =============================================================================
# Use this backend for Oracle Cloud deployments.
# State is stored in Oracle Cloud Object Storage (S3-compatible).
#
# Oracle Cloud Always Free Tier includes:
# - 10GB Object Storage (free forever)
# - Perfect for Terraform state storage
# =============================================================================

